    <w type="alerts-view" class="view">
      <w type="h1">Alerts</w>
<w type="p">Provide contextual feedback messages for typical user actions with the handful of available and flexible alert messages.</w>
<w type="h2">Examples</w>
<w type="p">Alerts are available for any length of text, as well as an optional dismiss button. For proper styling, use one of the eight required contextual classes (e.g., .alert-success).</w>

<w class="demo-box alerts-demo">
