<w type="h2">Dismissing</w>
<w type="p">Add a dismiss button and the [color=#bd4147][bgcolor=#fdf4f4] .alert-dismissible [/bgcolor][/color] class, which adds extra padding to the right of the alert and positions the [color=#bd4147][bgcolor=#fdf4f4] .close [/bgcolor][/color] button.</w>
<w type="p">On the dismiss button, add the [color=#bd4147][bgcolor=#fdf4f4] data-dismiss="alert" [/bgcolor][/color] attribute, which triggers the C functionality.</w>

<w class="demo-box alerts-demo">
  <w class="demo-preview-box"><alert class="alert alert-warning alert-dismissible">
  <strong class="mr-1">Holy guacamole!</strong>
  <text>You should check in on some of those fields below.</text>
  <button class="close" data-dismiss="alert">&#215;</button>
</alert></w>
